title: 3BR/2BA Townhome for Rent
posting_body: ['Welcome to the heart of Pico Rivera!', 'Located on a corner lot, step inside to see this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom unit.', 'This unit is the main unit in the front that has its own separate entrance and an extremely large family room!', 'With a fireplace in the living room, a fully remodeled bathroom, and laundry space, this unit is perfect for a family!', "Come see this cozy home before it's too late!", 'Back unit is also available for lease.', 'Strict NO-PET policy.', 'Deposit amount to be determined by credit score.', 'If score is 700 or above: $3,500, if below 700: $7,000.', 'Tenant pays flat rate of $350 for water, gas, electric, trash utilities.', 'Washer & dryer hook-up available.', 'Application link upon request.']
